messages.content: ComfyUI_AceNodes is a collection of useful custom nodes that are not included in the ComfyUI core.
Which primitive nodes are included in ComfyUI_AceNodes?
ComfyUI_AceNodes includes the following primitive nodes: Integer, Float, Text, and Seed.
What text nodes are available in ComfyUI_AceNodes?

ComfyUI_AceNodes provides various text nodes such as Text Concatenate, Text Input Switch (2 way, 4 way, 8 way), Text List, Text Preview, Text Selector, Text To Resolution, Text Translate, and Text Google Translate.
Which image nodes are included in ComfyUI_AceNodes?

ComfyUI_AceNodes offers several image nodes including Image Constrain, Image Remove Background, Image Color Fix, Image Question Answering, Image Load From Cloud, Image Save To Cloud, Image Get Size, and Image Face Crop.
What mask nodes are available in ComfyUI_AceNodes?
ComfyUI_AceNodes includes the Mask Blur node for working with masks.
Which audio nodes are provided by ComfyUI_AceNodes?
ComfyUI_AceNodes offers audio nodes such as Audio Load, Audio Save, and Audio Play.
What other nodes are included in ComfyUI_AceNodes besides primitive, text, image, mask, and audio nodes?
ComfyUI_AceNodes also includes other nodes like Expression Eval, Any Input Switch (bool), and Any Input To Any.
